description:
Our Partner in Madison, WI is seeking a Kofax KTA Software Engineer for a contract role – which has potential to become a permanent position! In this role, you’ll join a small dev team at a large Insurance Company headquartered in Wisconsin – however this role is open to full time remote (inc post-Covid).
Responsibilities include supporting/maintaining the current system, and well as building/configuring additional functionality to automate additional recognition, work-flow, and integration use cases. Additionally, an immediate task will be to upgrade KTA from version 7.4 to 7.7. The primary focus of this role is to work with KTA. Additional assignments within the ECM realm are possible.
A qualified candidate will be proficient with:

KTA installation and configuration;
KTA development;
Kofax Analytics;
C#.net;
SQL Server;
ability to effectively work with others and share knowledge.

Certification in KTA Essentials is highly desired.
